tagline: Source code for Miabot and Beluga ROS System
body:
Welcome to the documentation for the Princeton University Dynamical Control System Laboratory ROS project.

This software runs the lab's Beluga and Miabot multi-agent robotic test platforms. 

The following are links to the project's code documentation.

### ROS Packages

**dcsl_beluga_driver:** [dcsl_beluga_driver](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_beluga_driver/html/index.html)

**dcsl_high_level_control:** [dcsl_high_level_control](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_high_level_control/html/index.html)

**dcsl_low_level_control:** [dcsl_low_level_control](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_low_level_control/html/index.html)

**dcsl_messages:** [dcsl_messages](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_messages/html/index.html)

**dcsl_miabot_driver:** [dcsl_miabot_driver](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_miabot_driver/html/index.html)

**dcsl_miabot_main:** [dcsl_miabot_main](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_miabot_main/html/index.html)

**dcsl_state_estimator:** [dcsl_miabot_main](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_state_estimator/html/index.html)

**dcsl_swarm_director:** [dcsl_swarm_director](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_swarm_director/html/index.html)

**dcsl_vision_tracker:** [dcsl_vision_tracker](http://leonard-lab.github.com/dcslROS/html/dcsl_vision_tracker/html/index.html)
